spec_data.Name: eog-devel
spec_data.Description:
The Eye of GNOME image viewer (eog) is the official image viewer for the
GNOME desktop. This package allows you to develop plugins that add new
functionality to eog.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 09 Nov 2017 07:58:43 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Support for developing plugins for the eog image viewer
